How to Make Fried Ice Cream. If you like ordering
this tasty, hot-and-cold treat at restaurants,

00:00:09.550 --> 00:00:15.321
now you can whip it up yourself any time.
You will need 1 qt. vanilla ice cream 3 egg

00:00:15.321 --> 00:00:23.910
whites 3 c. crushed cereal Vegetable oil A
baking sheet Parchment paper An ice cream

00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:32.000
scoop Dessert dishes 3 c. cookie crumbs (optional)
3 c. sweetened coconut flakes (optional) 3

